title: Mirza-Hingis lift women's doubles title at Wuhan Open
text: Mirza-Hingis lift women's doubles title at Wuhan Open Saturday, 3 October 2015 (1 minute ago) *Wuhan, Oct. 3 (ANI): Indian tennis ace Sania Mirza and her Swiss partner Martina Hingis maintained their scintillating run as they clinched their seventh women's doubles title of the year at the Wuhan Open on Saturday.* Wuhan, Oct. 3 (ANI): Indian tennis ace Sania Mirza and her Swiss partner Martina Hingis maintained their scintillating run as they clinched their seventh women's doubles title of the year at the Wuhan Open on Saturday. The top seeded Indo-Swiss pair claimed a 6-2, 6-3 win over the Romanian pair of Irina-Camelia Begu and Monica Niculescu in the summit clash that lasted one hour and nine minutes. Mirza and Hingis have won seven women's doubles titles this year, including two Grand Slam titles at Wimbledon and the US Open, since joining forces in March. (ANI)
